{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textAncientPolis.png?t=1714113944\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/comingSpring.png?t=1714113944\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/timeLapse.gif?t=1714113944\" /><br>Take good care of your people, provide enough food, trade with your allies and wage wars against your enemies and definitely don't mess with the Greek gods!!<br><br>Lay the foundations for the first democracy, listen to your people and help them with their groundbreaking inventions.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textBuild.png?t=1714113944\" /> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/buildingGif.gif?t=1714113944\" /><br>Build your city for the &quot;normal&quot; population, for the aristocrats and the intellectuals. Make sure that everyone has a job and everyone has a roof over their heads, otherwise a lot of trouble will quickly arise!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textTheater.png?t=1714113944\" /> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/theaterGif.gif?t=1714113944\" /><br>Immerse yourself in ancient Greece. Organize plays that represent current issues in society<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textGods.png?t=1714113944\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/godImage.png?t=1714113944\" /><br>If there's one thing for sure, it's that you should always be good with the gods! Or bad will happen...<br>If you mess up with the gods, they will send some meteorites, bad thunderstormes or worse....<br>They'll also let you know, if they like you.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textScience.png?t=1714113944\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/scienceImage.png?t=1714113944\" /><br>Science is one of the most important things in ancient Greek. You need to guide your inhabitants! Give them the possibility to move the earth. Be the best in science.<br><br> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textTrade.png?t=1714113944\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/tradeGif.gif?t=1714113944\" /><br>If you don't have enough resources, there are 2 ways to get them.  Either you plunder and rob other polis or you start trade partnerships with allies. Which one you choose is up to you!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/textProtect.png?t=1714113944\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/wildAnimalsGif.gif?t=1714113944\" /><br>They may look peaceful and huggable, but they are very dangerous! You have to protect your residents from the dangerous wild animals!!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2329670?t=1714113944","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1714113944","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/capsule_231x87